texts.content: <font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>这个是在1966年</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>而spps呢这个技术就是在</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>这个1963年发明的</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>哎这个而大家也知道</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>我们现在的这个胰岛素</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>并不是通过化学而成</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>而是通过重组表达来获得了</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>所以这个关于哎</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>我们国家这个第一次路边讲擦肩而过</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>可能呃</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>大家知道这样的一些更多的科学背景</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>以后就会更加理解</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>这么一个遗憾是怎么回事</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>那么这个有了这个技术之后呢</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>就蛋白质</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>大家就开始从这个多肽向这个蛋白质</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>进发但是</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>随着这个氨基酸</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>这个残肌的数量的这个增加</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>这个的故乡合成的这个产率呢</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>他就呈指数型的这个下降</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>而且纯化难度是逐步的提高的</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>我们目前来说这个spps</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>经过这个从60年代发明到现在</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>他的这个已经优化到极致了</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>每一步反应他的这个收率</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>几乎都可以达到99%</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>但是大家可以想一想</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>当你合成一个氨基酸是百分99的时候</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>然后你的整个合成收率</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>当这个蛋白质是</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>超过50个的时候</size></color></font>

<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>他的收率就会下降到0.99的50次方</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>这就是非常小的一个数字了</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>而这还远远达不到我们蛋白质</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>的这个长度</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>通常来说</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>我们的一个蛋白质</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>大概是有300个氨基酸左右</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>那么</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>这个完全去合成这样的这个半歪指</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>这是一个不可想象的这个事情啊</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>大家也可以看到在这个左下图</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>这个是在2020年的</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>有这个我们的这个有一篇3S</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>的文章他们呢是发展了一个这个</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>微流控的技术</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>来进行一个长的</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>86个氨基酸的</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>这个胰岛素前体的这个合成</size></color></font>

<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>那么相比于这个这个传统的这个spps</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>就是我们在这个地方看到的</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>通过这个</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>传统方法</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>也合成86个残疾的这个胰岛素</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>它在叶像上</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>大家看到这个叶像上的这个风</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>他是多个峰</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>而且是一个宽峰</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>也就是说他有86个氨基酸的</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>也有85个84个的</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>然后这中间还有大量的错配的硝旋的</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>所有的这些东西混杂在一起</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>即使是你通过这种高压液象</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>这种精细的这个方法</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>都无法对这个产物进行这个分离了</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>所以在这个合成层长度上呢</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>它是由于我们存在一个临界点</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>那么目前我们要去实现</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>它的这个蛋白质的合成</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>怎么去做呢</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>我们就需要把这个目标蛋白</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>拆分成多个多肽的片段</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>然后每个片段呢</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>大概是20到40个氨基酸左右</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>这也是</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>这个大家去这个多肽合成公司</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>能够订购到的多肽</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>通常也就是这个这个长度范围</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>然后再把这些片段</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>通过这个合成之后</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>再进行这个顺次的这个拼接</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>所以大概是在90年代开始</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>整个领域的核心</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>就已经从合成这个全蛋白质</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>转向了如何我们把</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>这几十个氨基酸给它拼接起来</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>那么目前</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>最常用的这个多肽的这个拼接方法呢</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>是在90年代的时候</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>由这个芝加哥大学的</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>啊kent教授提出的</size></color></font>
<font id="" path="D:/Program Files/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"><color=(1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000, 1.000000)><size=5.000000>叫做所谓的自然化学连接法</size></color></font>
